* Save Structured (JSON) Results to RaceRoster.
*
*   When to use:    After the race to publish final structured results, or during the race for live updates.
*   How to use:     Double-click to upload all results to RaceRoster.
*
*   Setup:
*     Pass the RaceRoster sub-event ID below.
*     Example (direct):  ResultsOnline.rsm   297655
*     Example (Entries): ResultsOnline.rsm   %rr_5k%
*
*   Recommendation:
*     - If you publish both structured and unstructured results, use separate
*       RaceRoster sub-event IDs (e.g. %rr_5k% for structured, %rr_5k_u% for
*       unstructured). Define them once in Entries.INI rather than hardcoding IDs
*       in multiple listings and RSMs — this avoids forgetting to update one file.

ResultsOnline.rsm   %rr_5k%
